Yixi.

00:03:07.919 --> 00:03:08.928
Yixi.

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:19.840
I'm here.

00:03:26.039 --> 00:03:27.199
Chen, do you know?

00:03:30.360 --> 00:03:31.879
I've been thinking all this time.

00:03:32.680 --> 00:03:33.639
I hated them.

00:03:35.879 --> 00:03:38.120
I hated how they
treated me like a monster.

00:03:39.199 --> 00:03:40.800
I hated their beatings and curses.

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:44.039
All their looks were the same.

00:03:45.520 --> 00:03:47.000
If this world is so cruel,

00:03:48.039 --> 00:03:49.400
why should I protect them?

00:03:50.280 --> 00:03:51.719
Their lives mean nothing to me.

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:55.319
But your words

00:03:56.719 --> 00:03:58.439
made me realize
I couldn't lie to myself.

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:01.680
Deep down,

00:04:02.639 --> 00:04:05.039
I still yearn for their acceptance.

00:04:08.099 --> 00:04:09.340
I still want to live

00:04:10.199 --> 00:04:11.639
and protect the Three Realms.

00:04:19.399 --> 00:04:20.360
I'm sorry.

00:04:21.319 --> 00:04:22.839
If it weren't for me,

00:04:24.040 --> 00:04:26.319
you wouldn't have become like this.

00:04:27.439 --> 00:04:29.000
You are the Sword Master.

00:04:30.639 --> 00:04:32.439
You should've been your parents' pride.

00:04:33.540 --> 00:04:34.496
I understand you.

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:37.024
Yixi.

00:04:37.759 --> 00:04:38.784
I'm right here.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:41.279
Right here with you.

00:05:01.360 --> 00:05:02.336
Take a sip.

00:05:05.079 --> 00:05:06.879
It might calm the symptoms.

00:05:16.519 --> 00:05:17.568
Another sip.

00:05:17.759 --> 00:05:18.688
One more,

00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:20.352
and it'll subside.

00:05:29.680 --> 00:05:30.560
Better now?

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:37.079
- Stop!
- Stop!

00:05:37.568 --> 00:05:38.620
Wan Guchen,

00:05:38.620 --> 00:05:40.120
you brought this evil deity back,

00:05:40.779 --> 00:05:43.000
plunging Wanfeng into grave danger.

00:05:43.500 --> 00:05:44.899
