00:05:45.420 --> 00:05:46.368
You

00:05:46.620 --> 00:05:47.779
have nowhere to run.

00:05:48.779 --> 00:05:49.620
Wan Guchen,

00:05:50.300 --> 00:05:51.379
surrender quietly.

00:05:52.180 --> 00:05:53.056
We will

00:05:53.620 --> 00:05:55.420
grant you an intact corpse.

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:58.620
Yixi, don't be afraid.

00:06:28.259 --> 00:06:29.280
Yixi.

00:06:30.339 --> 00:06:31.660
Don't let the deity take over.

00:07:04.540 --> 00:07:05.472
Yixi.

00:07:06.379 --> 00:07:07.459
Stop this!

00:07:07.459 --> 00:07:08.620
No more senseless killing!

00:07:08.899 --> 00:07:09.740
