00:07:10.100 --> 00:07:11.379
Tell her to spare me!

00:07:12.220 --> 00:07:13.139
Guchen.

00:07:13.139 --> 00:07:14.939
I'm your own uncle!

00:07:16.300 --> 00:07:17.180
From now on,

00:07:17.180 --> 00:07:18.819
I won't compete with you for anything.

00:07:19.259 --> 00:07:21.139
Just make her spare my life!

00:07:21.339 --> 00:07:22.180
Guchen.

00:07:22.180 --> 00:07:23.759
Yixi, come down now!

00:07:23.779 --> 00:07:25.079
He's no threat to us.

00:07:25.699 --> 00:07:26.660
Come down!

00:07:53.500 --> 00:07:54.379
You cursed creature!

00:07:54.740 --> 00:07:55.648
How dare you return?

00:07:55.800 --> 00:07:56.680
You sinner!

00:07:56.800 --> 00:07:57.888
Get out!

00:07:58.740 --> 00:07:59.660
Get out!

00:07:59.980 --> 00:08:00.980
You walking calamity!

