00:21:09.039 --> 00:21:10.240
Could you help me?

00:21:11.392 --> 00:21:13.696
I'll reward you with this jade pendant.

00:21:15.680 --> 00:21:16.608
Miss,

00:21:16.608 --> 00:21:18.519
are you alone here?

00:21:20.660 --> 00:21:23.299
My father abandoned us when I was young.

00:21:24.279 --> 00:21:25.859
My mother and I relied on each other.

00:21:26.619 --> 00:21:27.619
But then

00:21:28.700 --> 00:21:30.099
she fell gravely ill

00:21:30.460 --> 00:21:31.488
and left me.

00:21:32.400 --> 00:21:33.240
How tragic.

00:21:34.119 --> 00:21:35.319
We know the way.

00:21:35.319 --> 00:21:36.256
Come with us.

00:21:36.759 --> 00:21:38.039
Yes, we'll guide you.

00:21:39.359 --> 00:21:40.279
Thank you.

00:21:40.640 --> 00:21:41.696
Let's go.

00:21:41.696 --> 00:21:42.656
Let's go!

00:21:43.160 --> 00:21:44.096
Fetch the cart.

00:21:45.152 --> 00:21:46.048
Slow down.

00:21:46.960 --> 00:21:47.808
Slow down.

00:21:56.319 --> 00:21:57.720
Is this the way out?

00:21:58.119 --> 00:21:59.960
Why does the mist keep thickening?

00:22:03.200 --> 00:22:04.759
Of course this isn't.

00:22:05.519 --> 00:22:06.559
If you leave now,

00:22:06.960 --> 00:22:09.319
how can we enjoy you?

00:22:24.240 --> 00:22:25.400
Ghost! Ghost!

00:22:25.519 --> 00:22:26.680
The taste is indeed good.

00:22:26.680 --> 00:22:27.559
Ghost!

00:22:27.559 --> 00:22:29.079
I'm pleased.

00:22:29.728 --> 00:22:30.759
Ghost! Ghost!

00:22:35.400 --> 00:22:37.079
Weren't you eager earlier?

00:22:38.119 --> 00:22:39.640
Why run now?

00:22:53.279 --> 00:22:54.559
Such potent vital energy.

00:22:55.920 --> 00:22:56.768
As expected,

00:22:57.599 --> 00:22:59.119
men's vile desires

00:22:59.480 --> 00:23:01.359
make excellent nourishment.

00:23:08.279 --> 00:23:09.200
Another one?

00:23:10.720 --> 00:23:11.776
Help!

00:23:12.519 --> 00:23:13.440
Is there anyone?

00:23:15.640 --> 00:23:16.576
Help!

00:23:16.960 --> 00:23:18.000
My foot hurts!

00:23:19.599 --> 00:23:20.640
Help!

00:23:20.640 --> 00:23:21.559
Is there anyone?

00:23:21.799 --> 00:23:22.680
Is there anyone?

00:23:27.240 --> 00:23:28.320
(Yixi,)

00:23:28.640 --> 00:23:29.599
(you really came back.)

00:23:32.960 --> 00:23:33.984
Sir.

00:23:34.119 --> 00:23:35.136
Help!

00:23:35.519 --> 00:23:36.400
Sir.

00:23:36.400 --> 00:23:37.240
Please help me.

00:23:37.720 --> 00:23:38.656
I'm so scared.

00:23:38.880 --> 00:23:39.920
I just saw over there,

00:23:40.279 --> 00:23:42.160
two people died horribly.

00:23:43.079 --> 00:23:44.039
Could you help me?

00:23:44.920 --> 00:23:46.359
Sir, please.

00:23:47.279 --> 00:23:48.160
Don't you know

00:23:49.559 --> 00:23:50.624
how they died?

00:23:54.480 --> 00:23:55.440
How should I know

00:23:56.079 --> 00:23:57.180
how they died?

00:23:59.240 --> 00:24:00.119
Why not

00:24:01.839 --> 00:24:03.420
join them?

00:24:09.400 --> 00:24:11.240
It's you causing trouble here.

00:24:13.119 --> 00:24:14.400
You're an immortal.

00:24:15.559 --> 00:24:17.000
No wonder I couldn't harm you.

00:24:19.079 --> 00:24:20.680
You are quite attractive.

00:24:21.420 --> 00:24:22.619
It'd be a shame

00:24:23.039 --> 00:24:24.032
to let you die.

00:24:25.039 --> 00:24:26.720
Why not let me enjoy you first?

00:24:28.119 --> 00:24:29.400
How dare you!

00:24:30.480 --> 00:24:31.559
Do you know who I am?

00:24:34.319 --> 00:24:36.279
Quite decent.

00:24:37.079 --> 00:24:38.279
How interesting.

00:24:40.319 --> 00:24:42.880
The more you push me away,

00:24:44.480 --> 00:24:46.319
the more intrigued I become.

00:24:48.799 --> 00:24:50.279
Let me see

00:24:50.720 --> 00:24:52.240
what you'll look like

00:24:52.920 --> 00:24:54.339
after breaking your rules.

00:25:01.980 --> 00:25:03.339
I'm afraid you'll be disappointed.

00:25:03.599 --> 00:25:05.559
You grow more fascinating by the minute.

00:25:06.920 --> 00:25:08.000
My name is Bai Chuli.

00:25:08.000 --> 00:25:09.216
Your name?

00:25:15.319 --> 00:25:16.359
Stop causing trouble.

00:25:18.640 --> 00:25:20.880
If you don't want me to do that,

00:25:22.240 --> 00:25:23.599
let's make a deal.

00:25:24.440 --> 00:25:26.359
Stay by my side forever,

00:25:27.279 --> 00:25:28.440
and I'll stop harming people.

00:25:29.039 --> 00:25:29.952
Deal?

00:25:30.799 --> 00:25:33.079
I've never seen someone so shameless.

00:25:34.819 --> 00:25:35.900
If you harm anyone again,

00:25:36.660 --> 00:25:37.859
I won't spare you.

00:25:39.779 --> 00:25:41.779
I've seen countless men's eyes.

00:25:42.779 --> 00:25:43.740
You can't fool me.

00:25:45.180 --> 00:25:47.059
You're clearly attracted to me.

00:25:50.579 --> 00:25:51.579
But that's fine.

00:25:52.460 --> 00:25:53.980
I enjoy challenges.

00:26:00.500 --> 00:26:01.420
Why are you here?

00:26:02.420 --> 00:26:05.180
That woman was the former Bai Yixi.

00:26:05.579 --> 00:26:07.259
So you found her after all.

00:26:07.819 --> 00:26:09.259
I've waited for 300 years.

00:26:11.619 --> 00:26:13.299
Now, I've finally found her.

00:26:14.140 --> 00:26:17.339
But do you know the Night Deity
still resides within her?

00:26:18.019 --> 00:26:19.660
When the Night Deity's power awakens,

00:26:20.059 --> 00:26:22.460
you must kill her
to protect the Three Realms.

00:26:25.059 --> 00:26:25.900
What did you say?

00:26:28.940 --> 00:26:30.940
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

00:26:32.859 --> 00:26:34.660
If I'd told you,

00:26:34.660 --> 00:26:37.700
you might not have waited for 300 years

00:26:37.700 --> 00:26:39.619
to kill the Night Deity again.

00:26:39.980 --> 00:26:40.980
If that's the case,

00:26:41.819 --> 00:26:43.460
I refuse to be the Sword Master.

00:26:44.539 --> 00:26:45.819
I won't harm her.

00:26:46.460 --> 00:26:47.819
This is her destiny.

00:26:49.380 --> 00:26:50.859
You can abandon your position.

00:26:51.099 --> 00:26:52.619
Others will take the role.

00:26:53.220 --> 00:26:55.059
She'll still die regardless.

00:27:00.099 --> 00:27:01.460
I've said my piece.

00:27:02.380 --> 00:27:03.539
Consider the implications

00:27:04.380 --> 00:27:05.859
carefully.

00:27:09.779 --> 00:27:10.720
Why?

00:27:13.140 --> 00:27:14.180
Why must it be this way?

00:27:17.140 --> 00:27:18.740
(Perhaps your greatest wish)

00:27:19.779 --> 00:27:21.740
(was to live freely and joyfully)

00:27:23.420 --> 00:27:25.220
(even if the ending
would remain unchanged.)

00:27:26.619 --> 00:27:28.339
(But I can't face you again.)

00:27:28.740 --> 00:27:29.859
(I can't kill you again.)

00:27:31.259 --> 00:27:32.940
(I won't let you endure the pain)

00:27:33.700 --> 00:27:35.539
(of being parted from the beloved.)

00:27:41.440 --> 00:27:42.880
Here you go, sir.

00:27:44.119 --> 00:27:45.059
This is yours.

00:27:47.579 --> 00:27:49.779
- Good.
- Good.

00:27:50.400 --> 00:27:51.680
Here, coming.

00:27:58.880 --> 00:27:59.904
Here you are.

00:28:05.599 --> 00:28:06.720
Madam Yu.

00:28:09.680 --> 00:28:11.079
You're here, Mr. Shiyi.

00:28:11.759 --> 00:28:13.160
What would you like?

00:28:13.799 --> 00:28:17.119
I'll take her tonight.

00:28:17.720 --> 00:28:19.400
No problem, Mr. Shiyi.

00:28:19.559 --> 00:28:21.359
She's yours this evening.

00:28:25.599 --> 00:28:26.680
- Good.
- Good.

00:28:27.160 --> 00:28:28.440
- Good.
- Good.

00:28:39.160 --> 00:28:40.416
Beautiful one.

00:28:40.512 --> 00:28:41.536
Quickly!

00:28:42.720 --> 00:28:44.160
Why so late?

00:28:44.880 --> 00:28:47.519
You kept me waiting.

00:28:48.920 --> 00:28:52.039
The finest things require patience.

00:28:55.599 --> 00:28:56.736
What are you...?

00:28:58.319 --> 00:28:59.599
So mischievous.

00:29:05.839 --> 00:29:07.160
Beauty.

00:29:07.680 --> 00:29:10.279
Don't waste the night.

00:29:11.160 --> 00:29:13.680
Let's get to bed quickly.

00:29:15.359 --> 00:29:17.160
Are you a monster?

00:29:19.200 --> 00:29:20.119
Mr. Shiyi.

00:29:20.720 --> 00:29:22.079
Have you forgotten me so soon?

00:29:23.680 --> 00:29:25.759
You personally chose me moments ago.

00:29:25.799 --> 00:29:26.640
I...

00:29:27.240 --> 00:29:28.480
I know nothing.

00:29:47.720 --> 00:29:48.768
Help!

00:29:48.880 --> 00:29:49.720
Help!

00:29:50.240 --> 00:29:51.559
Why is it you?

00:29:51.559 --> 00:29:52.680
So it's you.

00:29:53.640 --> 00:29:55.200
Seems fate truly binds us.

00:29:55.519 --> 00:29:56.759
Weren't you in Wanyingzhou?

00:29:57.960 --> 00:29:59.160
It's all for you.

00:30:01.880 --> 00:30:03.039
To find you,

00:30:03.279 --> 00:30:04.720
I've searched everywhere.

00:30:05.559 --> 00:30:07.160
How else would we meet again so soon?

00:30:07.660 --> 00:30:09.299
You promised to harm no one.

00:30:09.680 --> 00:30:10.688
Unforgivable.

00:30:13.559 --> 00:30:15.039
True. I did say that.

00:30:16.079 --> 00:30:17.279
But on one condition.

00:30:17.680 --> 00:30:19.480
You must stay by my side.

00:30:23.319 --> 00:30:24.599
Have you forgotten?

00:30:27.559 --> 00:30:28.512
So

00:30:29.359 --> 00:30:30.799
you're the one who killed them.

00:30:35.240 --> 00:30:36.480
Twisting logic.

00:30:36.920 --> 00:30:38.048
Shamelessly unrepentant.

00:30:41.599 --> 00:30:43.000
You think I won't kill you?

00:30:45.160 --> 00:30:46.160
How ridiculous.

00:30:46.680 --> 00:30:48.200
I am a member of the Night Clan,

00:30:48.680 --> 00:30:50.400
feeding on human desires.

00:30:51.359 --> 00:30:53.960
If they had all been noble like you,

00:30:54.680 --> 00:30:55.839
I couldn't have slain them.

00:30:59.599 --> 00:31:00.599
But you...

00:31:01.839 --> 00:31:04.559
As an Upper Immortal
who specializes in hunting our clan,

00:31:06.720 --> 00:31:08.000
why haven't you killed me yet?

00:31:09.960 --> 00:31:10.839
Unless

00:31:12.279 --> 00:31:13.519
